Class ObjectDetailsBeanInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.api.beans.ObjectDetailsBeanInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.BeanInfo

    public class ObjectDetailsBeanInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.beans.BeanInfo
    An object that describes the ObjectDetails bean and supports DWR serialization. Providing this class means DWR will not need to do reflection.
